text: Minori Yamamoto (born 14 October 1997) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * yamamoto- minori-of-japan * asian-games-water-polo-jakarta Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
